        <mxCell id="5JijLFjPTpslOKc9d2ji-37" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;PLC进行相应锁附逻辑&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="120" x="335" y="1480" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="5JijLFjPTpslOKc9d2ji-38" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;流程结束&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="130" x="330" y="1580" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="5JijLFjPTpslOKc9d2ji-46" edge="1" parent="1" source="5JijLFjPTpslOKc9d2ji-42" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;" target="5JijLFjPTpslOKc9d2ji-36">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="5JijLFjPTpslOKc9d2ji-42" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;PC写入拍照完成&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="130" x="330" y="1260" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="5JijLFjPTpslOKc9d2ji-49" parent="1" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;darkOpacity=0.05;align=left;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;注&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;1、如果收到PLC流程中止信号，上位机流程复位至最初状态&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;2、开始流程前PC和PLC要进行对方的配方号校验，如不一致则不开始流程并且报警提示&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;3、双方需收到对方的回复信号再进行下一步，并且收到后复位之前发送的信号&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;4、PLC实时的将机械臂位置写入对应地址&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;5、PC收到启动信号后需要把PLC的螺栓位置写到PC的螺栓位置上&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;6、PC流程中或有异常 要将视觉就绪置为False，能进行流程就置为True&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;7、PC流程中认为有异常或者硬件问题，将视觉报警置为True&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="200" width="600" x="-680" y="-40" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="5JijLFjPTpslOKc9d2ji-50" parent="1" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;darkOpacity=0.05;align=left;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;PLC先发送&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;1、配方号&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;2、位置号(从21起，21号为第一颗螺栓)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;3、视觉纠偏方式&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="90" width="270" x="655" y="265" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="5JijLFjPTpslOKc9d2ji-51" parent="1" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;darkOpacity=0.05;align=left;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;PC 回复后先初始化&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;1、所有位位置坐标&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="280" x="655" y="400" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="5JijLFjPTpslOKc9d2ji-52" parent="1" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;darkOpacity=0.05;align=left;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; text-align: center; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;如果收到PC盲打信号，则PC直接结束流程&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="270" x="660" y="525" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="5JijLFjPTpslOKc9d2ji-53" parent="1" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;darkOpacity=0.05;align=left;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; text-align: center; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;视觉拍照流程：需要拍几次 就执行几次&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="270" x="670" y="770" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="5JijLFjPTpslOKc9d2ji-54" parent="1" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;darkOpacity=0.05;align=left;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;写入目标位置：锁几个螺栓就在对应地址写入几组坐标&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;1、拍一锁一：只在该位置螺栓地址写入坐标&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;2、拍二锁N：写入所有位置坐标&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;3、拍N锁N：写入所有位置坐标&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="100" width="340" x="660" y="1020" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="5JijLFjPTpslOKc9d2ji-55" parent="1" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;darkOpacity=0.05;align=left;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;PC收到回复后复位&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;1、完成信号&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);&quot;&gt;2、OK/NG信号&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="90" width="270" x="670" y="1370" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
